  250 years ago 6 missionaries set out from Argos, none returned.
  One arrived in Tharbad.
	This quest will not be implemented as Zima is going to change
	domains. 
  Date 2768 TA: Tharbad still populated but already partly deserted.
  Small garrision, dunedain officers.
  Population about 1000, dunedain, dunlendings, few Rohirrim.
  The Long Winter was 10 years ago, the city has not yet recovered,
  disgruntled dunlending exiles settled here after the dunlendings
  were defeated by the Rohirrim in 2759 TA.
  The missionary converts a few dunlendings.
  They build a shrine in the forest outside the city.
  Some band of orcs destroys the shrine about 40 years later.
  The inter-domain quest has been cancelled, since Zima
  changed domains.
  Shrine and tomb to be coded by Zima.

